Package com.gieseckedevrient.smartcard

Interface Summary
SEService.CallBack Callback interface if informs that this SEService is connected to the backend system and it's resources.
 

Class Summary
Channel This class represents a basic or logical Channel that can be used for an APDU transfer from a phone application to a Secure Element.
Reader This class is a proxy class that represents a certain Secure Element Reader which is available within the phone system.
SEService This SEService realizes the communication to available Secure Elements on the phone.
Session This class represents a session to a secure element which is available within the phone system.
